Asset as Non Fungible Token Transfer Start
Phase1: Data Aggregation
Broadcast initimation to all the consented vehicles for Data Collection
Uploads the radar data according to the criteria by offchain
Phase2: Proof of Radar Data for Assets
Submits the Proof of the data transfered to the OEM Data Pool and initimates its completion
Collects the Raw data from the datapool and preprocesses it, submits the hash of the consolidated data as a proof ensuring the completion
After the final proof is submitted then the Oauth Acess token of the data pool is submitted to the platfform
Phase4: Offchain Transfer of Radar Data Oauth Acess Token
Offchain Worker submits the Oauth Access Token as a webservice request
Posting of the Oauth Access Token happens only when the individual proof of the vehicle and the final proof is submitted on chain
Acknowledges the reception of the Oauth Access Token to the datamarket
Phase3: Fund Transfer
Transfers the amount as a comission of Bid Facilitation process from the Escrow to the Vehicle OEM
Transfer condition needs the Vehicle_OEM to submit the proof and the Asset Oauth Access Token
Transfers the amount as a reward of the radar data sold from the escrow to the Vehicle A
Transfer condition needs the Vehicle to submit a valid data submitting the individual proof as well as the acknowledgement of the Vehicle_OEM
Phase4: Finalisation of Asset Transfer
Transfers the ownership of the Non Fungible Asset Token and finalises the Asset Transfer
Phase5: Review of Asset Transfered
Submits the review of the data transferred as Non Fungible Asset Token
Review of the Non Fungible Asset Token helps in valuing the fidelity of the actors.
Asset as Non Fungible Token Transfer End
